cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper deals with image-to-image translation using GANs and meta-learning, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also proposes a novel approach for few-shot learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments are conducted on hair color attribute synthesis tasks, which can be categorized under computer graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
